creator: Mohamad Bzeih
descriptionHtml:
World's Key application is an interactive educational application for a set of curricula for Kindergarten and Primary Levels in the English language and Science.

In our schools, each student receives and uses printed books in his/her class in addition to an online account to access the mentioned application. This application provides students with audio-visual lessons in addition to conducting interactive exercises and assessments to all lessons in both subjects- English and Science.
descriptionShort: World's Key application is an interactive educational application.
